{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_2x0f9sd7mpjkfqtgb7dsu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"137384152","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-21T17-57-52-415Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a Map-based storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with a Map-backed store.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\nReturns an object with the following methods:\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value associated with the given key from the cache.\n\n```javascript\nconst value = cache.get(key)\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache for the given key. Returns the stored value.\n\n```javascript\nconst result = cache.set(key, value)\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the value associated with the given key from the cache.\n\n```javascript\nconst success = cache.delete(key)\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5348,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":5248},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc54d6fe-4f71-486b-b18e-26fe6b05e0d0","uuid":"1066aae7-e155-4ab6-96ca-463dbff7afb5","timestamp":"2026-07-22T02:04:27.453Z"}
